<title>klạmnjy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- klạmnjy wklạmy ktyr wḥyạty mn gẖyr tạ̉tẖyr

[V2]
 wlsạny ʿmạl bylkẖbṭ wạ̉nạ fạkr nfsy kdh kbyr

[V3]
 ạlqrạr- yạ rb sạʿdny ạ̉tklm wklạmy yṣbḥ lh ṭʿm

[V4]
 wkạ̉nh bmlḥ mrsẖwsẖ wlạ ạ̉qwl klmạt mạlhạsẖ ṭʿm

[V5]
 2- wsạʿạt ḥạjạt ạ̉kbr mny brḍh bạqdm fyhạ rạ̉yy

[V6]
 ạ̉ḥyạnaⁿạ bạṭlʿ mkswf ạ̉w wạḥd yṭlʿ yjrḥny

[V7]
 3- wạ̹lhy kẖlq ly wdnyn wkẖlq ly bs lsạn wạḥd

[V8]
 wbkdh ạ̉nạ hạsmʿ ḍʿfyn wạ̉tklm blsạny ạlwạḥd</lyrics>
</song>